Package: libreotp
Version: 1.2.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libsecret-1-0, libjsoncpp26 | libjsoncpp25 | libjsoncpp1
Maintainer: Henri Cook <libreotp@henripub>
Description: LibreOTP - A Desktop App for 2FAS
 LibreOTP is a cross-platform desktop OTP code generator that works with
 exported JSON files from 2FAS. It supports both encrypted and unencrypted
 2FAS exports with secure password storage for encrypted backups.
 .
 Features:
  - Support for 2FAS group organization
  - Search functionality across all codes
  - Secure password storage for encrypted backups
  - Cross-platform compatibility
